14
00:01:39,090 --> 00:01:45,900
♫  For only you are my heaven ♫

15
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:51,760
[Goodbye My Princess]

16
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:56,670
[Episode 49]

17
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:19,100
If Young Lord continues to drink like that, you'll make yourself drunk.

18
00:02:19,100 --> 00:02:22,640
Just blame MIss Mi Luo's wine for tasting so good like always,

19
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:25,930
I couldn't help but drink a few more cups.

20
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:32,830
It's the Spring Lantern Festival today.

21
00:02:32,830 --> 00:02:35,790
The emperor and the crown prince will both go out of the palace to climb up the city tower.

22
00:02:35,790 --> 00:02:38,940
Don't you need to organize the security?

23
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:45,340
Look at the festive occasion outside.

24
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:50,100
Everyone is chatting and laughing with others while hiding away their secret thoughts.

25
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:53,290
Even the emperor must forget the border turbulence tonight

26
00:02:53,290 --> 00:02:56,810
and stand atop the tower to put on an act that all is well.

27
00:02:57,560 --> 00:03:02,320
Then, why can't I drink a few cups here by myself, sneaking a moment of leisure?

28
00:03:03,830 --> 00:03:06,230
I think you are already drunk.

29
00:03:06,230 --> 00:03:11,380
Perhaps, you haven't been here for long and are not used to my strong wine.

30
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:18,480
Last time I came, it was with the crown princess consort. It has been a long time.

31
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:23,050
Xiaofeng indeed hasn't been here in a while.

32
00:03:23,050 --> 00:03:26,200
Is it because she is too busy to get away from the palace?

33
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:32,890
I don't know where she is either. The crown princess consort has disappeared for quite some time.

34
00:03:32,890 --> 00:03:37,460
No one knows if she is even alive or dead. The Yulin Palace Guards have searched the whole city.

35
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:39,900
They can't even find this one woman.

36
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:45,860
So, you are worried about work.

37
00:03:47,110 --> 00:03:52,580
Shangjing City is big but not too big. The person you want to find will appear sooner or later.

38
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:59,840
If you drink more, you'll really be drunk.

39
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:02,400
I'll go make some sobering tea for you.

40
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:07,120
Or else, there may be big trouble at the Spring Lantern Festival today.

41
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:25,010
[Mi Luo Drinking House]

42
00:04:25,010 --> 00:04:29,400
Other than the Singing Jade Brothel, that's the only place I've stayed in Shangjing.

43
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:34,320
I want to visit her. Let's go.

44
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:03,690
Your wine is as good as it's always been.

45
00:05:03,690 --> 00:05:06,750
There are many people who are complimenting my wine today.

46
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:10,700
I'm sure of that. People who come here must be wine connoisseurs like me.

47
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:15,210
All right! If you like it, I'll give you a few jars that you can take with you.

48
00:05:15,210 --> 00:05:18,050
Mi Luo, sit down.

49
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:24,130
From now on, I won't be able to come anymore.

50
00:05:24,130 --> 00:05:26,540
Why? Who dares not let you come?

51
00:05:26,540 --> 00:05:30,020
I'm going home, back to the Xi State.

52
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:35,210
So this time, I'm here to say farewell to you.

53
00:05:35,210 --> 00:05:38,670
But will they let you leave?

54
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:43,400
This is not the same as sneaking out from the palace to drink.

55
00:05:46,300 --> 00:05:49,300
I sneaked out this time. No one knows.

56
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:54,290
I'm only telling you. You need to keep my secret.

57
00:05:55,100 --> 00:06:00,780
That's for sure. But have you really decided to leave everything here?

58
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:13,150
Xiaofeng, you need to know that

59
00:06:13,150 --> 00:06:18,100
in this cold capital, there will be people

60
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:22,000
secretly caring about you in places that you can't see,

61
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:25,550
worrying about you.

62
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:36,160
That doesn't matter anymore. When I return to my Xi State, going back to my world,

63
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:41,150
there won't be any Shangjing, or Eastern Palace,

64
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:44,500
or a person who is making me sad.

65
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:49,830
You used to drink and make merry, looking like there was not a single worry.

66
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:52,800
I thought you had already let go of your worries.

67
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:55,690
I'll continue to drink wine and make jokes,

68
00:06:55,690 --> 00:07:00,040
because I've found my most important person.

69
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,550
Don't worry.

70
00:07:06,730 --> 00:07:09,350
You can finally go home.

71
00:07:10,230 --> 00:07:14,600
Mi Luo, if you come to Xi State, you have to come and find me first.

72
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:17,940
Hiding in Shangjing,

73
00:07:17,940 --> 00:07:22,400
being an owner of a wine house for the rest of my life,

74
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,900
I'm actually quite content.

75
00:07:26,410 --> 00:07:30,230
Perhaps, this place makes me feel at ease.

76
00:07:30,230 --> 00:07:34,600
Isn't feeling at ease the reason why you want to go home?

77
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:38,990
Mi Luo, for someone so carefree like you,

78
00:07:38,990 --> 00:07:44,510
you'll be fine wherever you are. Here. Cheers to you.

79
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:48,090
- Here! Cheers to everyone!
- Let's toast the Mi Luo's Drinking House!

80
00:07:48,090 --> 00:07:50,160
- All right!
- Cheers!

81
00:08:13,390 --> 00:08:19,150
Young Lord, you better drink some sobering tea. If you keep drinking like this, the wine will stay with you beyond tomorrow.

82
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:25,460
There's a practice from my hometown.

83
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:28,500
One can use the leftover wine stain under your cup

84
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:32,630
to make a prediction on how the person you are thinking now

85
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:34,710
is doing.

86
00:08:36,460 --> 00:08:39,800
How do you explain this wine stain?

87
00:08:40,570 --> 00:08:45,500
The wine stain under your cup is evenly spread out.

88
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:50,400
That means, the person you are thinking about now

89
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:56,190
is safe. She might be currently doing what she wishes to do.

90
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:02,680
Mi Luo, I hope you are not lying to me.

91
00:09:03,650 --> 00:09:07,190
If you believe then there is.

92
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:28,080
Sometimes, I really do wish that she can leave Shangjing.

93
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:33,640
Only once she leaves this place, can she probably be truly safe.

94
00:09:37,460 --> 00:09:42,170
The divination symbol already indicates that she is now safe.

95
00:09:42,170 --> 00:09:46,300
Besides you, there is still someone protecting her with his life.

96
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:35,380
Your Imperial Highness.

97
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:21,860
Your Imperial Highness, does this gown fit me well?

98
00:11:22,830 --> 00:11:24,190
It's pretty.

99
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:29,290
Crown Prince, please put the hairpin on Related Lady of Excellence.

100
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,680
Xiaofeng.

101
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,130
Hairpin?

102
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:23,500
It's an old tradition for the husband to put a hairpin on his wife during the Spring Lantern Festival.

103
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:28,290
Implying that the couple will be loving forever.

104
00:12:38,070 --> 00:12:39,610
I will put it on you.

105
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:02,770
It's too odd for me to wear this while I am in man's clothes.

106
00:13:05,250 --> 00:13:06,950
I will keep it instead.

107
00:14:17,900 --> 00:14:20,400
I heard that the emperor and noble consort have gone up the city tower.

108
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:24,640
This noble consort is acting on behalf of the empress position. She might be crowned as the empress soon!

109
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,540
Be careful of what you say.

110
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:43,750
His Imperial Majesty is up the city tower!

111
00:14:45,650 --> 00:14:47,430
It's really the emperor!

112
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:50,290
Your Imperial Majesty and Noble Consort!

113
00:14:50,290 --> 00:14:52,400
This is indeed bestowing bountiful blessings on us.

114
00:14:56,580 --> 00:14:58,600
It's so beautiful to look at!

115
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:11,390
In the twenty-sixth year of Tiantong, the country is in prosperity, its fortune abundant,

116
00:15:11,390 --> 00:15:15,000
laws are strictly implemented, families and tribes are in harmony,

117
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:19,900
there is an honest and cultured atmosphere, efficient governance and peaceful people,

118
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:23,960
there is just and dutiful officials, and good relationships with foreign states. At this Shangyuan Festival,

119
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:27,370
we celebrate with all the people in the world.

120
00:15:27,370 --> 00:15:33,400
We pay respect to the gods and ancestors above, and pray for blessings of our citizens.

121
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:56,240
Let me go, Li Chengyin! Let me go!

122
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,900
Fireworks...

123
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:32,970
This is the first time that I find these fireworks pretty to look at.

124
00:16:32,970 --> 00:16:37,800
I used to think it was too noisy and extravagant. For a momentary sparkle,

125
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:43,680
too many efforts have to be spent. I thought it was very wasteful. But now, I suddenly feel that

126
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:48,430
people really need a short moment of luxury.

127
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:54,860
Looking at a sky with full blooming flowers, we can temporarily forget our pains.

128
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:59,700
Allow the heart's innermost happiness, no matter how little it is, to be unleashed.

129
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,430
Xiaofeng!

130
00:17:14,360 --> 00:17:15,390
Release the arrows!

131
00:17:15,390 --> 00:17:19,500
Listen to me! Assassin, if you let her go now, I'll let you leave safely.

132
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:25,620
If you hurt my wife at all, I will flay you into a thousand pieces so that you'll die in pain.

133
00:17:25,620 --> 00:17:28,600
I'll do as promised, just like this arrow!

134
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:38,860
I'm sorry.

135
00:17:41,130 --> 00:17:42,900
Why are you saying sorry?

136
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:46,800
I've finally realized...

137
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:53,800
that here in Shangjing, I've been living within a scam.

138
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:58,300
In this scam, I have been

139
00:17:58,300 --> 00:18:00,500
in love with a liar.

140
00:18:04,700 --> 00:18:06,580
Xiaowu, I'm sorry.

141
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:13,100
I shouldn't be hesitating up until now, and not bearing to part with this place.

142
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:15,020
Then, let me ask you again.

143
00:18:15,930 --> 00:18:19,040
Are you willing to return to Xi State with me now?

144
00:18:23,100 --> 00:18:29,220
Take me away quickly. I don't want to stay here anymore.

145
00:18:29,220 --> 00:18:30,890
All right.

146
00:18:30,890 --> 00:18:35,200
Golden money during a time of peace! The emperor's graces are so vast!

147
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:38,780
Long live His Imperial Majesty!

148
00:18:38,780 --> 00:18:42,200
Long live His Imperial Majesty!

