00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:57,260
Long live His Imperial Majesty!

153
00:18:57,260 --> 00:19:01,100
Long live His Imperial Majesty!

154
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:05,900
Long live His Imperial Majesty!

155
00:19:05,900 --> 00:19:09,050
Long live His Imperial Majesty!

156
00:19:14,130 --> 00:19:17,680
Imperial Father! Imperial Father! I've discovered the crown princess consort.

157
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:20,730
I plead that you close the gates and capture the assassin.

158
00:19:23,530 --> 00:19:29,100
Today is the Spring Lantern Festival. Doing that will cause panic among the people.

159
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:32,700
Imperial Father, if we don't shut the gates now, the assassin will run away with the crown princess consort.

160
00:19:32,700 --> 00:19:35,690
Trying to capture them after that is like looking for a needle in the sea.

161
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:50,080
Long live Your Imperial Majesty!

162
00:20:10,300 --> 00:20:15,200
Long live Your Imperial Majesty!

163
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:21,420
Long live Your Imperial Majesty!

164
00:20:25,320 --> 00:20:26,690
Imperial Father!

165
00:20:26,690 --> 00:20:27,910
- Imperial Father! Hurry!
- Your Imperial Highness.

166
00:20:27,910 --> 00:20:32,350
Hurry, Imperial Father, return to the palace with Noble Consort Gao now!

167
00:21:08,900 --> 00:21:10,620
Hurry!

168
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:16,900
Your Imperial Highness, go back to the palace with me!

169
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:17,760
Let me go!

170
00:21:17,760 --> 00:21:19,750
Don't go there.

171
00:21:21,710 --> 00:21:22,540
Your Imperial Highness!

172
00:21:22,540 --> 00:21:23,640
- My Lady!

173
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:25,390
Your Imperial Highness!

174
00:21:25,390 --> 00:21:26,370
You few, come with me!

175
00:21:26,370 --> 00:21:27,920
- Yes!
- Your Imperial Highness!

176
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:46,390
Xiaowu!

177
00:22:13,770 --> 00:22:15,370
Xiaowu!

178
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,650
Xiaowu!

179
00:23:45,620 --> 00:23:47,560
Let me go!

180
00:23:49,700 --> 00:23:51,270
Xiaofeng!

181
00:23:53,660 --> 00:23:55,320
Xiaofeng!

182
00:24:48,890 --> 00:24:50,340
Go back with me.

183
00:25:21,010 --> 00:25:22,950
Xiaofeng!

184
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:28,570
Who are you?

185
00:25:32,420 --> 00:25:34,510
I am Gu Xiaowu.

186
00:25:34,510 --> 00:25:35,880
Gu Xiaowu. Gu Xiaowu.

187
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:56,170
Gu Xiaowu.

188
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:12,900
Xiaowu!

189
00:26:20,230 --> 00:26:22,630
Grandpa!

190
00:26:35,600 --> 00:26:37,690
I will kill you!

191
00:26:39,130 --> 00:26:43,080
Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng!

192
00:26:48,490 --> 00:26:50,280
Who are you?

193
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:52,420
It's me who should be asking who you are.

194
00:26:52,420 --> 00:26:57,700
I am the fifth prince of Li Empire, Li Chengyin.

195
00:27:05,950 --> 00:27:08,560
Crown Princess Consort, you are awake.

196
00:27:10,250 --> 00:27:13,200
