197
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:17,460
Crown Princess Consort? Crown Princess Consort!

198
00:27:18,210 --> 00:27:19,610
Xiaofeng!

199
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:26,980
Xiaofeng. Xiaofeng?

200
00:27:37,490 --> 00:27:40,720
Xiaofeng, what's the matter?

201
00:27:44,300 --> 00:27:46,230
It's me.

202
00:27:47,900 --> 00:27:49,910
I am Chengyin.

203
00:27:49,910 --> 00:27:53,400
Xiaofeng. Xiaofeng, I am Chengyin.

204
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:55,450
I am Chengyin, Xiaofeng.

205
00:27:55,450 --> 00:27:57,120
I am Chengyin.

206
00:27:57,120 --> 00:28:00,440
- Go away.
- You... What's the matter?

207
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:02,410
I am Chengyin.

208
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:06,600
Xiaofeng, it's me! I am Chengyin!

209
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:09,360
Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng!

210
00:28:10,710 --> 00:28:15,540
Xiaofeng... Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng...

211
00:28:15,540 --> 00:28:18,590
- Quick, get the imperial physician! Hurry!
- Yes.

212
00:28:35,600 --> 00:28:41,220
Qu Xiaofeng, why did you come back?

213
00:28:41,220 --> 00:28:45,330
Why? Why?!

214
00:29:26,460 --> 00:29:28,360
Imperial Father.

215
00:29:28,360 --> 00:29:30,070
No need for bows.

216
00:29:31,890 --> 00:29:33,920
Thank you, Imperial Father.

217
00:29:43,410 --> 00:29:47,380
Xiaofeng, the imperial physician said you've been traumatized.

218
00:29:47,380 --> 00:29:51,500
The wound on your head is just mild. It's not a big problem. Don't worry.

219
00:29:52,330 --> 00:29:54,590
Thank you, Imperial Father.

220
00:29:54,590 --> 00:30:00,740
Xiaofeng, why did you suddenly appear at the Vermillion Bird Gate?

221
00:30:02,820 --> 00:30:04,890
The assassin took me there.

222
00:30:04,890 --> 00:30:08,250
Why did he take you there?

223
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:20,930
Do you remember what he looks like?

224
00:30:30,460 --> 00:30:35,100
You spent a few days with him. You don't recall his face?

225
00:30:35,100 --> 00:30:41,150
He wore a mask all the time and wouldn't talk to me.

226
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:50,970
Where did you hide these past days?

227
00:30:51,820 --> 00:30:54,300
I am not sure.

228
00:30:56,270 --> 00:31:02,990
Sometimes in the woods. Other times in a rundown temple.

229
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:08,570
I don't know those places.

230
00:31:09,730 --> 00:31:14,450
That assassin took you to hide in so many places,

231
00:31:14,450 --> 00:31:16,820
but didn't hurt you.

232
00:31:16,820 --> 00:31:19,590
What did he really want?

233
00:31:34,130 --> 00:31:38,970
Xiaofeng, you frequently go to Singing Jade Brothel.

234
00:31:38,970 --> 00:31:42,740
Have you heard about a man named Sun Er?

235
00:31:47,700 --> 00:31:49,630
Sun Er?

236
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:56,220
No, I haven't.

237
00:31:59,410 --> 00:32:04,750
All right. You've had a hard time. Rest well first.

238
00:32:04,750 --> 00:32:08,370
If you remember anything, especially if it's about the assassin,

239
00:32:08,370 --> 00:32:11,220
tell me immediately.

240
00:32:13,020 --> 00:32:17,120
Thank you, Imperial Father. I understand.

241
00:32:40,870 --> 00:32:44,080
Why are you still obsessed?

242
00:32:44,080 --> 00:32:49,360
I'm not obsessed. I've already thought it through clearly.

243
00:32:50,800 --> 00:32:54,030
If you are really clear about it, then you should know

244
00:32:54,030 --> 00:32:56,750
the crown princess consort doesn't belong to you!

245
00:32:56,750 --> 00:33:01,630
It's true she doesn't belong to me, but she doesn't belong to anyone, either.

246
00:33:02,290 --> 00:33:06,550
She should return to Xi State and live her original life.

247
00:33:09,370 --> 00:33:12,570
What else really belongs to me in this world?

248
00:33:12,570 --> 00:33:17,250
I don't even belong to myself.

249
00:33:21,080 --> 00:33:22,670
Godfather,

250
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:32,360
I've completed what I was supposed to do. Please let me go.

251
00:33:34,220 --> 00:33:35,890
What did you say?

252
00:33:38,290 --> 00:33:42,350
Please release me and let me go.

253
00:33:48,590 --> 00:33:54,530
Crown Prince, what do you think about what the crown princess consort said.

254
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:58,430
She's been traumatized and her head was injured.

255
00:33:58,430 --> 00:34:01,660
It's normal that she can't explain things in detail.

256
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:06,390
Besides, she doesn't have to defend an assassin.

257
00:34:08,270 --> 00:34:10,610
During the Shangyuan Festival, everyone knows that

258
00:34:10,610 --> 00:34:14,720
the security at the Vermilion Bird Gate is the strictest.

259
00:34:14,720 --> 00:34:18,180
Why didn't the assassin choose another gate

260
00:34:18,180 --> 00:34:21,610
and insisted to take such a great risk?

261
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:26,310
For that assassin daring to break into the Singing Jade Brothel to assassinate someone,

262
00:34:26,310 --> 00:34:28,500
I already thought it was particularly inexplicable.

263
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:31,690
And now, he dared to charge through the Vermilion Bird Gate.

264
00:34:31,690 --> 00:34:36,170
He must have thought he was invincible in martial arts and couldn't be stopped by regular guards.

265
00:34:37,490 --> 00:34:40,050
It's truly suspicious.

266
00:34:41,280 --> 00:34:45,510
If Gao Yuming really wanted to assassinate Mingyue,

267
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:48,750
there were actually hundreds and thousands of opportunities.

268
00:34:48,750 --> 00:34:53,460
Why pick the time when I was there?

269
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:57,060
If his target was me,

270
00:34:57,060 --> 00:34:59,370
why did he

271
00:34:59,370 --> 00:35:04,210
then give up this extraordinary opportunity?

272
00:35:05,080 --> 00:35:08,850
What are your deductions then, Imperial Father?

273
00:35:08,850 --> 00:35:11,800
I am very confounded, too.

274
00:35:12,660 --> 00:35:18,650
At any rate, that assassin must not get away.

275
00:35:18,650 --> 00:35:22,260
We also must find the plotter behind him.

276
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:23,680
Yes.

277
00:35:24,750 --> 00:35:27,760
Do you know what you are saying?

278
00:35:31,070 --> 00:35:36,140
When I was young, I thought that all these things were just my own problems.

279
00:35:36,140 --> 00:35:42,220
No matter how painful it was, how suffocating it was, it was what I deserved to endure.

280
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:47,670
Until you involved Xiaofeng. She had to bear the loss of all of her family,

281
00:35:47,670 --> 00:35:51,390
the loss of her memories, and the pain of losing the people she loves. Is that fair to her?

282
00:35:51,390 --> 00:35:53,460
Is this what you mean by great justice?

283
00:35:53,460 --> 00:35:59,300
Jian'er, this is fate.

284
00:35:59,300 --> 00:36:03,960
Even if we didn't involve her, Danchi would have perished anyway.

285
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:07,270
Xiaofeng would have still been stuck in the palace struggle. Isn't that fate?

286
00:36:07,270 --> 00:36:11,040
Then the Gu family being completely annihilated, was that the will of Heaven, too? Was it also fate?!

287
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:12,610
I...

288
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:25,680
Godfather, I used to believe

289
00:36:27,330 --> 00:36:29,760
that I was Xiaofeng's hero.

290
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:34,290
But later, I discovered that

291
00:36:36,060 --> 00:36:38,550
I had already become

292
00:36:39,350 --> 00:36:42,390
a liar who spouted lies.

293
00:36:42,390 --> 00:36:47,070
I became a killer whose hands were full of blood.

294
00:36:48,670 --> 00:36:51,350
I don't want to live that kind of life anymore.

295
00:37:03,980 --> 00:37:05,220
[Bearing Graces Hall]

296
00:37:05,220 --> 00:37:07,520
Crown Princess Consort, have a sip of porridge.

297
00:37:07,520 --> 00:37:10,820
I followed a recipe and took the time to make it.

298
00:37:10,820 --> 00:37:15,600
Crown Princess Consort, for my sake, please take a sip.

299
00:37:18,490 --> 00:37:24,190
Crown Princess Consort, do you want the sweet lotus porridge first or the salty roasted meat porridge?

300
00:37:32,660 --> 00:37:34,300
I don't want any.

301
00:37:36,140 --> 00:37:37,990
Crown Princess Consort.

302
00:37:39,430 --> 00:37:41,300
Leave.

303
00:37:43,130 --> 00:37:44,790
Yes.

304
00:38:11,130 --> 00:38:13,280
I've remembered everything.

305
00:38:16,740 --> 00:38:18,870
Everything.

306
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:22,950
I've remembered all of it.

307
00:38:26,110 --> 00:38:28,490
A'Du, you knew about it. Right?

308
00:38:31,030 --> 00:38:34,590
Whistle arrow, Teacher, white-eyed wolf king,

309
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:43,190
the battle at Danchi, Dad's tears, Grandpa's fresh blood,

310
00:38:46,540 --> 00:38:50,040
and the bone-chilling water of the River of Oblivion.

311
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:53,450
Everything, everyone,

312
00:38:53,450 --> 00:38:56,190
you clearly know all about it. Right?

313
00:39:10,700 --> 00:39:13,960
Yes, Princess.

314
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:22,600
A'Du, you can talk.

315
00:39:27,820 --> 00:39:30,350
Didn't your larynx get injured? You...

316
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:36,670
You've been pretending.

317
00:39:39,900 --> 00:39:44,100
Because I made a terrible pledge to the gods.

318
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:51,930
Then, why didn't you tell me?!

319
00:39:51,930 --> 00:39:56,210
Why did you hide the truth from me?! Why must you be like everyone else

320
00:39:56,210 --> 00:39:58,220
hiding things and lying to me?!

321
00:39:58,220 --> 00:40:02,490
Why did you treat me this way?! I've only thought of you as my closest family!

322
00:40:06,520 --> 00:40:10,780
Princess, I couldn't mention even a single word to you.

323
00:40:10,780 --> 00:40:16,090
It's because this was the only way that I could stay by your side to protect you!

324
00:40:16,090 --> 00:40:18,550
The past is too cruel.

325
00:40:18,550 --> 00:40:21,470
I didn't want you to recall any of that painful past!

326
00:40:21,470 --> 00:40:24,990
Then, am I not in pain now?!

327
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:29,390
I feel even more guilty now!

328
00:40:29,390 --> 00:40:33,160
I have to live next to my nemesis every day.

329
00:40:33,160 --> 00:40:39,420
Every day, I have to see my feelings toward him sinking more and more, unable to extricate myself!

330
00:40:40,530 --> 00:40:42,600
Am I now not in pain?

331
00:40:42,600 --> 00:40:45,760
Can you bear to see me like this now?

332
00:40:46,860 --> 00:40:51,300
Why did I forget and then have to remember them?!

333
00:40:51,300 --> 00:40:55,230
Why did even the River of Oblivion have to lie to me, too?

334
00:41:19,700 --> 00:41:24,150
Do you remember me teaching you swordplay when you were young?

335
00:41:24,150 --> 00:41:27,300
Your arm must be stable. Your eyes must be sharp.

336
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:32,060
When you stab, you must be fast and ruthless.

337
00:41:32,060 --> 00:41:37,640
You wanted to compete with me in swords, but you always lost. But you said,

338
00:41:38,460 --> 00:41:40,990
