339
00:41:40,990 --> 00:41:42,740
I remember.

340
00:41:52,890 --> 00:41:56,460
If you win, you can sleep two extra hours.

341
00:41:56,460 --> 00:42:01,100
If you win, you can leave.

342
00:42:47,680 --> 00:42:51,200
Godfather, I'm sorry.

